1. *Pojas* oko struka mi je pretesan. (The *belt* around my waist is too tight.)
2. Moram kupiti novi *pojas* za haljinu. (I need to buy a new *sash* for my dress.)
3. Njihov dom je smešten u *pojasu* visokih planina. (Their home is located in the *belt* of high mountains.)
4. Lekar mi je rekao da treba da nosim *pojas* za leđa. (The doctor told me that I should wear a *back brace*.)
5. Policajac je opremio automobil *pojasima* za spasavanje. (The police officer equipped the car with *safety belts*.) 
6. Ova knjiga pripada *pojasu* svetske književnosti. (This book belongs to the *realm* of world literature.)
7. *Pojas* zemlje oko reke je veoma plodan. (The *strip* of land around the river is very fertile.)
8. Nije preporučljivo da vozite bez *pojasa*. (It is not recommended to drive without a *seat belt*.)